title: Three Dog Night singer Cory Wells dies - 4029TV.com
text:
There are 1 comment on the 4029TV.com story from 2 hrs ago, titled Three Dog Night singer Cory Wells dies . In it, 4029TV.com reports that:
Cory Wells, one of the lead singers in the popular '60s and '70s band Three Dog Night, has died, the band said Wednesday. "It is with deep sadness and disbelief that I must report the passing of Cory Wells, my beloved bandmate for over 45 years," said fellow Three Dog Night singer Danny Hutton in a statement on the band's website, threedognight.com.
